00:57:52,120 --> 00:57:54,640
We're talking about
Cheongmun University.

498
00:57:54,754 --> 00:57:58,220
As for rebate, it's customary.
Is that even news?

499
00:57:58,325 --> 00:58:02,870
The known figure is over 3 billion won. There
are hundreds of doctors who were bribed.

500
00:58:02,880 --> 00:58:05,465
-Does it make sense to help them?
-It doesn't make sense, but...

501
00:58:06,590 --> 00:58:12,439
But... this makes sense...

502
00:58:15,580 --> 00:58:16,420
What is this?

503
00:58:16,420 --> 00:58:20,380
Eul, just this once. Please turn a
blind eye to it just this once.

504
00:58:20,480 --> 00:58:22,849
It's not even a hard thing to do.

505
00:58:23,830 --> 00:58:28,488
Freedom of media shouldn't kneel
down in front of capitalism.

506
00:58:30,557 --> 00:58:33,250
But you know, the operation
fee we spent all this time...

507
00:58:33,393 --> 00:58:36,880
After you pay for assistant director,
you must not have much left.

508
00:58:36,890 --> 00:58:37,631
That's right.

509
00:58:38,010 --> 00:58:39,633
You should have some, too, CEO...

510
00:58:39,800 --> 00:58:41,468
Not me. Forget about me.

511
00:58:41,940 --> 00:58:47,510
As for me... tada! This will do it.

512
00:58:47,520 --> 00:58:50,310
It's a foreign car! Lucky you!

513
00:58:51,444 --> 00:58:53,146
Sunbae, are you taping this okay?

514
00:58:53,670 --> 00:58:54,614
Tape what?

515
00:58:56,450 --> 00:58:59,619
There's a hidden camera here, say hi!

516
00:59:00,450 --> 00:59:02,556
-Hey, No Eul...
-Thank you.

517
00:59:03,360 --> 00:59:06,893
Thanks to your testimony, I think I can tie
it in with the media news at Cheongju.

518
00:59:07,890 --> 00:59:10,363
Take this back and don't get it stolen.

519
00:59:10,964 --> 00:59:11,831
You punk!

520
00:59:11,831 --> 00:59:20,094
(You did well today)

521
00:59:36,250 --> 00:59:40,393
Right? I did really well today, right?

522
00:59:55,040 --> 00:59:57,077
Let's see each other again tomorrow, Jun Young.
